description: Things get worse for Schaefer and his partner, Rasche, as Rasche discovers the existence of a whole fleet of Predators ready to invade and Schaefer comes face-to-face with the Colombian drugs lords! Also, general panic continues in New York as the Predators hunt for Schaefer and kill everyone in their path!
name: Predator

description: Schaefer and Rasche are reunited at last, but it's just in time to fight the battle of their lives! It's all-out war against the Predator army, and since the army and police want Schaefer and Rasche out of the way--the two must turn to one of their enemies for the manpower they need! Will anyone--or anything-- be left standing when the smoke clears?
name: Predator

description: Newly weaned off her medication, Blythe heads back to work for the first time in weeks. A surprise is waiting for her: the Hyperwing 307, the sleekest and most advanced hyperprax airship ever built. It will be hers to fly – if she survives a series of baffling pilot's tests.
name: Reveille
Operazione al Cervello
The Fifth Mad Report on Spy vs Spy

volume.name: Fifth Mad Report on Spy vs Spy

description: it only took the god-emperor Charon ten thousands years to conquer his entire universe and forge the stellar empire known as THE NEGATION  . but omnipotent isn't enough. Charon now casts his baleful eye across the gulf between realities... and he covets the bright and thriving worlds in our cosmos. so it is that one hundred ill-fated souls have been abducted from scores of worlds across our galaxy. they have been brought to His dark realm to be watched and tested. to struggle and die. and the answers yielded by their sacrifice will be key to the coming conquest unless one man sees his predicament for what it is,and turn the tables on a mad god...
name: Prequel

description: Big Bang’s plan seems to be working perfectly. In the company of Professor Titus, he reaches Fog Peak, but Mister No is on their trail. Together, the three discover the unsettling Valley of the Dead, which kills whoever has the misfortune to cross it!
name: La Valle dei Morti

description: In Bahia, Mister No meets his old friend Miranda, who wants to get to Nova Canudos, to the headquarters of Geraldo Ribeiero, a sort of guru who has a notable following among the wretches of Sertão. Ricardo, Miranda’s fiancée, is also a follower of Geraldo: but Nova Canudos is not paradise, it is hell on earth!
name: Il Profeta

description: Nova Canudos has shown its true face: Father Otavio, a priest who has been trying to persuade Geraldo’s followers to leave the sect, has been savagely murdered. Cruel Ricardo, Miranda’s fiancé, gets Mister No arrested. And Miranda is about to be raped by the Blessed Geraldo!
name: La Tela del Ragno

description: The reign of the Blessed Geraldo is over: the government troops have invaded and now Nova Canudos is in flames! Mister No and Miranda are believed to be among Geraldo’s followers and an execution platoon is being prepared for Jerry!
name: Plotone d'Esecuzione

description: Brenda Lood and Sammy Taylor, Mister No’s new friends, are, in reality, two spies for a foreign power! They have stolen a microfilm containing extremely important data and Jerry is entrusted by the American government with the task of recovering it …
name: Missione Uragano

description: Brenda Lood and Sammy Taylor have escaped to Santo Domingo, where Mister No has found a job as a pilot for the Weather Bureau. But Jerry discovers that his real enemies are not the two spies that he was looking for…And, to save himself, he will have to fly right in the eye of cyclone!
name: Nell'Occhio del Ciclone

description: The Tariana Indios are in revolt and leading them is a mad individual who has taken over Makakaraua, a terrible masked ritual. The Tarianas attack the missionaries present in the zone; Mister No, with Father Herrera and Father Sanchez, tries to stop them…
name: Il Dio Vendicatore

description: The Van Helsens’ evangelical mission center has been attacked by the Tarianas, who have murdered the minister’s wife and son. But Mister No continues his investigations, until he manages to discover the surprising identity of the leader of the Tarianas!
name: Maschera Tragica

description: Cliff, a pilot who dies in an aeroplane accident, leaves Mister No a diary, which however is stolen from him by a group of criminals. Our hero investigates and a mysterious character called Sanford asks to be taken to the Amazonian region of Urucú...
name: Il Segreto del Diario

description: Mister No receives a warm welcome from some of the Indios, who lead him to a village in which the huts are like the skyscrapers of New York and where there are sculptures in the form of taxis and televisions. In this strange world, Jerry is treated like a god. All thanks to a bizarre scientific experiment from several years before…
name: Il Villaggio dei Dannati

description: Komodo is an island in the Sonda sea, where the Dutch millionaire Jan Emmen has set up a gigantic tobacco plantation. But dramatic things happen - murdered men, disappearing animals, houses pulled up from their foundations…- phenomena which Mister No and Esse-Esse have to throw some light on.
name: I Delitti del Mar della Sonda

description: The mystery of Komodo is about to be revealed by Mister No and Esse-Esse. An unsuspected character, who organises arms trafficking on the island, makes use of a personal army and of the terrible Buaya Darat, descendants of the ancient dinosaurs…and, like Tyrannosaurus Rex, hungry for human flesh!
name: I Draghi di Komodo

description:
A collection of the Return of Superman story line.
 
 After the death and funeral of Superman, multiple Supermen start appearing in Metropolis, all of them claiming to be the Man of Steel (well, not all of them, but we'll get to that later). There's Cyborg Superman, Superboy, Steel, and Eradicator. While the people aren't sure who is who, we quickly find out that Superboy is a clone of Superman, Steel is just a man trying to honor Metropolis's fallen hero, Eradicator is an age-old Kryptonian being sent to save the last of the Kryptonians, and Cyborg-Superman has something more sinister up his sleeve, as he works with Mongul to reshape Coast City in his image. The reader quickly comes to find out that the real Superman is back in action. After a long battle and Eradictor sacrificing himself, both Cyborg Superman and Mongul are defeated, and the real Superman reclaims his thrown. Everything is back to normal once again.
name: TPB

description: "ASSAULT ON NEW OLYMPUS," Finale! IT ALL COMES DOWN TO THIS! The past two years of storylines in Incredible Hercules have been building to one climactic moment, and here it arrives at last! The final showdown between Hercules and Typhon! Amadeus Cho becomes a true hero at last! And just why was Athena so happy at the end of "Sacred Invasion," anyway? All secrets are revealed in what is undoubtedly the most shocking ending of the year! Don't tell the Internet why we had to call this issue "EVERYBODY DIES!" PLUS! A bonus backup story featuring the AGENTS OF ATLAS!
name: Assault On New Olympus, Finale: Everybody Dies; Godmarked, Pt. 5: To Battle A God

description: Octavius has come to accept his new body, and Peter is of no use to him anymore. Now The Spider finds himself and his new flame surrounded by monsters happy to shed their humanity. Will he lose his too -- and how will this affect the world of the future? Don't miss the riveting conclusion to this breakout series! Based on the 1602 series from Neil Gaiman.
name: The Web Complete: Chapter 5

description: What could be more fun for detective John McClane than investigating robberies in New York City's finest massage parlors? How about dealing with a citywide blackout? Are things ever easy for this guy? This comic is brought to you by the words "smash" and "grab." Join legendary industry creator Howard Chaykin in this new ongoing on a thrill ride that's rung up over $1 billion in box office worldwide and become the gold standard for classic action! Yippee Ki Yay!
name: Year One Part Six

description: Beloved cartoonist Sergio Aragones writes, draws, and provides the cover for his first full-length Simpsons Comics issue. Springfield is on the brink of a nuclear meltdown (what else is new?) and Homer must do everything in his power to save the plant, the town, and his family from what is basically all his fault! Brace yourself for some serious silliness in 'No Cause For Alarm!'
name: No Cause For Alarm

description:
The all-new continuing Tick series continues with a second smash issue! A new super-villainess is is giving The Tick a 'run for his money' across the length and breadth of The City after stealing a super-powered 'mystery object.'
 
Plus, Chairface attempts to from the 'prison with prison' in which he has been incarcerated, due to his many previous escape attempts!
name: Heart of Glass

description: Her name is Abigail Freemantle. She is the oldest woman in America, born in 1882. And a terrible task has been placed before her: Tired and frail as she is, she must stand against Randall Flagg and the gathering forces of evil. As Mother Abigail reflects on her life's choices and prepares for visitors to Hemingford Home, she must face down the first attack from the dark man's minion...Spanning decades, it's the secret origin of one of Stephen King's greatest creations, True Believers!
name: Soul Survivors, Part 4

description: Here it is Farscape fans...one of the biggest secrets of the series revealed! Since the first issue of the smash hit comic book you've seen that something is not quite right with Crichton and Aeryn's son. Why? Be sure not to miss the stunning revelation in this fourth issue of the new ongoing FARSCAPE series written by the show creator Rockne O'Bannon!
name: Tangled Roots, Part 4: Baxx in the High Life Again
